cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with the structure of text and its content. It could also belong to "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it proposes an extension of LDA, a popular machine learning algorithm. Additionally, it could be categorized under "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as it evaluates the performance of the proposed model using text classification tasks. "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible sub-category as topic modeling is a popular technique in AI research. Finally, "cs.DS" (Data Structures and Algorithms) could be a relevant sub-category as the paper proposes a modification to an existing algorithm.
